# API Endpoint Tests
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or run with curl

### Health Check
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/webhooks/health

### Test Auth (will fail without token)
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_JWT_TOKEN

### Dashboard Summary (requires auth)
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_JWT_TOKEN

### Check Shop (requires auth)
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/shops/check
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_JWT_TOKEN

### Get Items (requires auth)
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/items
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_JWT_TOKEN

### Get Staff (requires auth)
GET https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/staff
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLERK_JWT_TOKEN

### Webhook Test (requires test key)
POST https://thingira-pos.vercel.app/api/webhooks/test
Content-Type: application/json
X-Test-Key: YOUR_WEBHOOK_TEST_KEY

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "clerkUserId": "user_test123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}
